{"summary":"The Block Research was commissioned by Ava LabsAva Labs and the Solana Foundation to produce Comparing Layer-1 Platforms: 2022 Edition, which provides an in-depth study across ten dominant Layer-1 (L1) ecosystems: Algorand, Avalanche, BNB Chain, Cardano, Cosmos, Ethereum, NEAR, Polkadot, Solana, and Tron. In this report, we compare their technical designs, network architectures, on-chain and ecosystem data, fundraising histories, and more. Through quantitative and qualitative analysis, we draw insights into what the future of the broader smart contract landscape could look like over the coming years. ","webName":"theblock.co","link":"https:\/\/www.theblock.co\/post\/199146\/comparing-layer-1-platforms-2022-edition-presented-by-solana-foundation-and-ava-labs","publishDate":"2023-01-04T14:06:08","id":90,"type":null,"title":"Comparing Layer-1 Platforms: 2022 Edition- Presented by Solana Foundation and Ava Labs","category":["SPONSORED"],"content":["<span class=\"TextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">The Block Research was commissioned by <\/span><\/span><a class=\"Hyperlink SCXW180621823 BCX0\" href=\"https:\/\/www.avalabs.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW180621823 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-charstyle=\"Hyperlink\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Ava <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-charstyle=\"Hyperlink\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Labs<\/span><\/span><\/a><span class=\"TextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"