data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">, Cosmos, Ethereum, NEAR, <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Polkadot<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">, Solana, and <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">T<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">ron<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">.<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> In this report, we compare their technical designs, network architectures, on-chain and ecosystem data, fundraising histories, and more. Through quantitative and qualitative analysis, we draw insights <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">into <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">what the future of the broader smart contract landscape could look like over the coming years.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:200,&quot;335559739&quot;:200,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-stringify-type=\"bold\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">The Block Research has created \u201CComparing Layer-1 Platforms: 2022 Edition\u201D presented by Solana Foundation and Ava Labs. To access the full report in PDF format, please fill out the form below:&nbsp;<\/b>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">TL;DR<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:200,&quot;335559739&quot;:200,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Many smart contract blockchains built using novel technologies have seen significant user adoption in the past few years. <\/span><span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Currently, research and development activity is largely focused on scaling blockchain technologies to accommodate potentially billions of regular users. Several scaling approaches are being experimented on across smart contract platforms:&nbsp;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:200,&quot;335559739&quot;:200,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Entities that interact with smart contract platforms can be divided into two groups \u2013 developers that build and deploy blockchain-enabled decentralized applications (DApps) as well as the community of end users that interact with the said DApps.&nbsp;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:200,&quot;335559739&quot;:200,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Major takeaways for DApp end-user communities across ecosystems:<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:200,&quot;335559739&quot;:200,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Major takeaways for DApp development activity:<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:200,&quot;335559739&quot;:200,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Outlook and challenges for the smart-contract platform landscape:<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559738&quot;:200,&quot;335559739&quot;:200,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","© 2023 The Block. All Rights Reserved. This article is provided for informational purposes only. It is not offered or intended to be used as legal, tax, investment, financial, or other advice."],"entity":[{"type":"Solana Foundation","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Solana<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-charstyle=\"Hyperlink\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> Foundation","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Cardano","content":"PERSON"},{"type":"2023","content":"DATE"},{"type":"Ava Labs","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Block Research","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"BNB","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Cosmos","content":"LOCATION"},{"type":"Ava <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW180621823 BCX0\" data-ccp-charstyle=\"Hyperlink\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Labs","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Polkadot","content":"LOCATION"},{"type":"1","content":"DATE"},{"type":"Solana","content":"PERSON"},{"type":"Ethereum","content":"LOCATION"}],"hashtag":[],"authors":["Dipankar Dutta","The Block"]}